rComments: Dr. Bataille is down-to-earth and evidently shares the same frustration that many do with regards to environmental issues. His teaching is good, and his evaluations ensure that you fully understand the material. He made meaningful connections with those who participated synchronously, and took constructive criticism from students.

Make sure you attend or watch all his lectures! He explains concepts very well and as a 5th year biology student, I applied a lot of knowledge I learned from previous courses into this course. He was very accommodating and susceptible feedback, easily one of the best profs I had at uO. He is very kind and reaches out when you need it. 10/10

Excellent prof! Il transmet très bien la matière du cours et prend son temps à répondre aux questions des étudiants. Il y a beaucoup de slides et de matière couverte à chaque cours mais tout de même intéressant :)
